"""
BLiTzBLiT Player (bbplayer) is an intuitive, Vim-navigable terminal player
for internet radio and SoundCloud. It utilizes a simple TOML file for
station management and leverages ffplay alongside yt-dlp for rock-solid
playback. SoundCloud tracks are automatically cached locally to prevent
streaming glitches, featuring an optional auto-advance mode for
uninterrupted listening.

Navigate with vim-style j/k/gg/G, press Enter to select/play, and toggle
continuous auto-advance for SoundCloud track lists with c.
"""

